I worked on the brand strategy for **C&S Paper Vietnam**, a market-entry and brand localization project for one of China’s largest household paper manufacturers. The goal was to help the brand enter Vietnam with a stronger emotional and strategic foundation, moving beyond category-generic claims like softness and price to establish a more differentiated **“premium accessible”** position. The final output was a strategic brand proposal and guideline system designed for long-term use across **e-commerce platforms like TikTok Shop and Shopee** as well as **modern retail channels such as WinMart, Aeon, and Circle K**.
